### ============================================
### WEBHOOK TESTS - THANH TOÁN
### ============================================
### Thay {{uuid1}} bằng UUID chiến dịch thực tế
### ============================================

### ============================================
### Test 11: WEBHOOK NGÂN HÀNG - Nhận thanh toán 1
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/webhooks/bank
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-2026-001",
  "amount": 5000,
  "campaignId": "{{uuid1}}",
  "description": "Donation for campaign",
  "senderName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "senderAccount": "1234567890"
}

